title: Architect, earthquake survivor leads reconstruction of childhood neighborhood
description: A young architect who lost eight relatives in the Feb. 6, 2023, disaster is now spearheading rebuilding efforts in her hometown, helping restore the community where she was raised.
content:

de: Der Architekt und Überlebende des Erdbebens leitet den Wiederaufbau des Viertels, in dem er aufgewachsen ist. Eine junge Architektin, die bei der Katastrophe am 6. Februar 2023 acht Verwandte verloren hat, leitet nun die Wiederaufbaubemühungen in ihrer Heimatstadt und trägt dazu bei, die Gemeinde, in der sie aufgewachsen ist, wiederherzustellen.
en: Architect, earthquake survivor leads reconstruction of childhood neighborhood. A young architect who lost eight relatives in the Feb. 6, 2023, disaster is now spearheading rebuilding efforts in her hometown, helping restore the community where she was raised.
la: Faber, terrae motus superstes ducit restitutionem infantiae viciniae. Iuvenis architectus qui octo propinquis in die 6 mensis Februarii anno 2023 amisit, clades nunc hastae in patria sua reficienda laborat, adiuvans ut communitatem restituat ubi evectus est.
